# Design System

## Colors

### CSS Variables (Primary)

All color values should use these CSS variables defined in `:root`:

| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-----------|-------|
| `--text` | `#6b6375` | `#9ca3af` | Body text, default text color |
| `--text-h` | `#08060d` | `#f3f4f6` | Headings, high-contrast text |
| `--bg` | `#fff` | `#16171d` | Background color |
| `--border` | `#e5e4e7` | `#2e303a` | Borders, dividers |
| `--code-bg` | `#f4f3ec` | `#1f2028` | Code blocks background |
| `--accent` | `#aa3bff` | `#c084fc` | Accent color (purple) |
| `--accent-bg` | `rgba(170, 59, 255, 0.1)` | `rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.15)` | Accent background tint |
| `--accent-border` | `rgba(170, 59, 255, 0.5)` | `rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.5)` | Accent border color |
| `--social-bg` | `rgba(244, 243, 236, 0.5)` | `rgba(47, 48, 58, 0.5)` | Social section backgrounds |
| `--shadow` | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0 10px 15px -3px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0 4px 6px -2px` | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0 10px 15px -3px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 0 4px 6px -2px` | Box shadows |

